{"tid":1931415,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港外國記者會要求特區政府澄清外媒記者在港工作情況","createTime":"2020-03-18T07:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T19:24:32.000Z","uid":41818,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a970770e9109dbb98c9d30fb26ad027fd8c8dee0","tid":1931415,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:03:41.000Z","msg":"香港外國記者會表示，關注中國外交部宣布針對美國駐華媒體的措施，強調香港在自己的制度下，法例確保擁有新聞自由；在《基本法》下，香港對外國人的工作簽證，包括記者，都是由香港入境處處理，如果制度有改變，代表一國兩制嚴重被侵蝕。<br />\n<br />\n外國記者會認為，特區政府必須馬上澄清相關情況，及確保外國記者及申請到香港工作的人士，不受中國政府的干預下，繼續獲得工作簽證。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部凌晨宣布，因應美國打壓中方媒體駐美機構的行為，決定採取多項反制措施，要求《紐約時報》、《華爾街日報》、《華盛頓郵報》年底前記者證到期的美籍記者，10日內交還記者證，今後不得在內地包括港澳繼續從事記者工作。\t\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515257-20200318.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515257-20200318.htm&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=8682c329\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515257-20200318.htm&h=37e85a98\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515257-20200318.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6cca8170e70e2cc14a51d60a956c5fb3cc67b725","tid":1931415,"uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"一國兩制幾時宣佈死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b181ea30558e33988f13f148dae609cc0380791","tid":1931415,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca8f0bc3924893c4c5e5a0a76daa9d7379caadf","tid":1931415,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:06:39.000